  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The LRA is drafting policy with respect to the application of tax legislation. Furthermore, the LRA is involved in litigation. These tasks require special skills in drafting texts that are clear, easily understandable and precise. This 5-day course was designed to improve the skills of participants in this field. The course combined theory and practice with a lot of time allocated to case studies.</narrative>
